&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Paxos, we are creating the infrastructure for a new, open financial system - one that anyone can access and participate in, and that operates efficiently. There are billions of people in the world who are unbanked or underbanked, and trillions of dollars that are locked up because of the inefficiencies of the legacy system. We envision a new system that allows any asset to move instantaneously, anywhere in the world - to unlock the potential of assets and people everywhere. Our customers include some of the biggest enterprises in the world like PayPal, Credit-Suisse and Societe Generale, and together we are upgrading the global financial system using modern blockchain and crypto technology.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Director of Compliance (Internal Controls and Governance) to join our rapidly growing company and Compliance team. This individual will be responsible for overseeing and scaling our Compliance governance and controls program and processes as related to managing Paxos company-wide policies, procedures, and regulatory obligations. This includes working closely with Paxos’ business line leads to ensure controls are appropriately documented and in place along with ensuring associated policies and procedures are up-to-date. Additionally, this individual will be critical in supporting strategic projects that are high priority and cross functional in relation to regulatory affairs and new business developments. This cross functional role will be a key to Paxos’s success as we continue to grow our business. Paxos will rely on this position to assist in implementing regulatory requirements within a new business entity and to adapt and apply policies, procedures, and controls.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As Director of Compliance (Internal Controls and Governance), you&#39;ll get to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ensure compliance and governance standards are implemented across all Paxos business lines and legal entities, including policies and procedures along with risk and compliance frameworks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Oversee the development and implementation of policies and procedures for all Paxos entities and operations engaging with cross-functional stakeholders and subject matter experts as necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and implement Paxos-wide compliance policies, including anti-bribery, conflict of interest, and internal trading policy and restrictions, ensuring and documenting compliance with those policies, and providing appropriate training&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Inventory, track, and manage updates and reviews for all Paxos policies and procedures, including appropriate record-keeping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Oversee development and completion of necessary Company-wide training&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Report to senior management, internal audit, and regulators regarding policy and training development and implementation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Oversee and coordinate systems access controls, including audit and maintenance of those controls, collecting and leveraging, data as appropriate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Identify and evaluate internal control deficiencies along with opportunities for efficiency wins; provide recommendations for improvement and monitor remediation efforts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Stay abreast of compliance and governance developments and their impact on Paxos’ Compliance programs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Assist in the preparation of annual regulatory examinations, internal audits and other external evaluations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Immerse yourself in blockchain technology, cryptocurrency for enterprises and investors, our regulation-first approach, and more&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your experience should include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;7+ years experience in consulting, project management or regulatory affairs management role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to manage stakeholders across the organization to drive mission critical projects to completion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to write clear and concise documentation and correspondences for regulatory projects&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understanding of how to manage various types of projects from kick-off to completion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A strong management presence and ability to rally the team around project needs and deadlines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to get your hands dirty and create leverage on projects by bringing your unique expertise and willingness to learn the moving parts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A bachelor&#39;s degree in business, technology or related field&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience in FinTech or financial services is a plus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong writing capabilities and experience with engaging regulators / auditory examiners a plus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
